{"mode": "overwrite", "content": "{
 "dialogue": [
  {
    "speaker": "SPEAKER_00",
    "text": "Welcome to the Rational Reminder Podcast. We're joined by Dr. Charles Chafin, whose work bridges psychology and financial planning.",
    "emo_text": "Friendly and informative",
    "emo_alpha": 0.6,
    "source_segment_ids": ["seg_000", "seg_0004"]
  },
  {
    "speaker": "SPEAKER_02",
    "text": "Thanks for having me.",
    "emo_text": "Grateful and warm",
    "emo_alpha": 0.6,
    "source_segment_ids": ["seg_0005"]
  },
  {
    "speaker": "SPEAKER_00",
    "text": "To start, what role does psychology play in financial planning?",
    "emo_text": "Curious and engaged",
    "emo_alpha": 0.6,
    "source_segment_ids": ["seg_0006"]
  },
  {
    "speaker": "SPEAKER_02",
    "text": "Psychology explains why clients behave the way they do with money. It bridges technical advice and real-world behavior.",
    "emo_text": "Explanatory and thoughtful",
    "emo_alpha": 0.6,
    "source_segment_ids": ["seg_0007"]
  },
  {
    "speaker": "SPEAKER_01",
    "text": "How do cognitive biases and heuristics affect financial decision-making?",
    "emo_text": "Inquisitive and analytical",
    "emo_alpha": 0.6,
    "source_segment_ids": ["seg_00014"]
  },
  {
    "speaker": "SPEAKER_02",
    "text": "Cognitive biases are helpful shortcuts, but they create systematic errors like overconfidence or loss aversion that get in the way of rational thinking.",
    "emo_text": "Explanatory and pragmatic",
    "emo_alpha": 0.6,
    "source_segment_ids": ["seg_00015"]
  },
  {
    "speaker": "SPEAKER_01",
    "text": "How does our environment shape our financial psychology?",
    "emo_text": "Curious and probing",
    "emo_alpha": 0.6,
    "source_segment_ids": ["seg_00022"]
  },
  {
    "speaker": "SPEAKER_02",
    "text": "Our environment is critical—creating friction for unwanted behaviors and eliminating friction for desired ones. Who we're around and the information we engage with also shape our financial psychology.",
    "emo_text": "Insightful and descriptive",
    "emo_alpha": 0.6,
    "source_segment_ids": ["seg_00023"]
  }
 ]
}"}

